</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1302,1437,1546,1573]" pageId="6" pageNumber="5" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[192,1440,1479,1641]" pageId="6" pageNumber="5">
<keyLead pageId="6" pageNumber="5">
— Elytra elongate in dorsal view, central disc flattened in lateral view, humped at base; elytral color pattern series of distinct spots and bands....................................................... 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1423,1437,1614,1640]" pageId="6" pageNumber="5">2</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="6" pageNumber="5">
