<emphasis bold="true" box="[850,975,1723,1750]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="5">pulcricolor</emphasis>
Skelley and Gasca-Álvarez
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1302,1437,1723,1750]" pageId="6" pageNumber="5" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[192,1440,1656,1817]" pageId="6" pageNumber="5">
<keyLead pageId="6" pageNumber="5">
— Pronotum lacking discal mark along posterior lateral margin; elytra parallel-sided, moderately humped near base............................................................................ 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1423,1437,1791,1817]" pageId="6" pageNumber="5">3</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
